            <title>Version 0.5.4</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's New in v0.5.4</h2><ul><li>**Microphone permission guard** — Recording now verifies microphone permission is granted before starting. If permission was revoked or never granted, shows a clear error and re-requests permission instead of silently failing.</li><li>**Audio input entitlement** — Added `com.apple.security.device.audio-input` entitlement for improved compatibility with recent macOS updates.</li></ul>]]></description>
